          "slidetitle": "When Humans Must Step In",
          "subtitle": "Recognising the moments that matter most",
          "slidecontent": "• Complaints escalating beyond scripts\n• Guests showing clear distress\n• Complex, multi-part requests\n• Sensitive personal circumstances\n• Repeated failed bot interactions"
